cutting through the gym.

01:39.866 --> 01:42.936
- Hey, sorry about that, kid.
- ( groans )

01:42.969 --> 01:46.673
This has been another
live report for KKTY.

01:46.706 --> 01:49.309
Okay, Zack,
you're on the air.

01:49.342 --> 01:51.878
What?
I was just on the air.

01:51.911 --> 01:54.614
No you weren't.
I just flipped on the switch,
dummy.

01:54.647 --> 01:57.117
Turn it off, bonehead,
I'm done.

01:57.751 --> 01:58.985
Excuse me?

01:59.019 --> 02:01.121
You're perfect,
you don't need any excuses.

02:01.154 --> 02:03.089
Can you tell me where
a Coach Sonski is?

02:03.123 --> 02:05.258
I'm here to try out
for the wrestling team.

02:05.291 --> 02:07.861
- But you're a girl.
- Gosh, you're quick.

02:09.596 --> 02:12.098
