- All right, men,

02:12.132 --> 02:15.869
everybody trying out for
the wrestling team
line up over here.

02:16.770 --> 02:18.605
Have your sign up cards ready.

02:19.072 --> 02:20.607
That's my cue.

02:22.709 --> 02:26.112
- Rodriguez, welcome back.
- Thanks, Coach.

02:26.146 --> 02:29.149
Anderson, whoa,
you gotta lose some weight.

02:30.183 --> 02:34.154
- AC, my man, my star.
- Hey.

02:34.187 --> 02:35.989
Are we gonna
beat Valley next week?

02:36.089 --> 02:38.758
