- Group: Yeah.

02:40.927 --> 02:43.663
Kristy Barnes.
( laughs )

02:43.697 --> 02:47.200
That's cute, honey.
This is a gym, not a Jane.

02:49.102 --> 02:52.906
Why don't you go
upstairs to home ec
and bake us some brownies?

02:52.939 --> 02:56.209
