I wanna try out for the team.
I'm as good as anybody here.

02:56.242 --> 02:58.144
Yeah, sure, toots.

02:58.178 --> 03:00.347
Coach,
are you saying you aren't
gonna let Kristy try out

03:00.380 --> 03:04.050
- simply because of her sex?
- Yeah,
the wrestling team's for guys.

03:04.050 --> 03:06.286
You wanna wrestle
with the girls, date 'em.

03:07.954 --> 03:09.589
That's not fair!

03:09.622 --> 03:11.958
I don't have hair
and that's not fair either.

03:14.327 --> 03:16.062
All right, men.

03:16.096 --> 03:19.065
Hit the mats, I gotta pick
a team to beat
Valley next week.

03:22.268 --> 03:24.704
It's wrong.
They won't even
give me a chance.

03:24.738 --> 03:27.874
I'm Zack Morris and I'm gonna
help you get that chance.

03:27.907 --> 03:30.343
Guys, I want you to meet
Kristy Barnes.

03:30.377 --> 03:31.778
- Hi, Kristy.
- Nice to meet you.

03:31.811 --> 03:34.948
She needs our help.
Coach won't let her try out
for the wrestling team.

03:34.981 --> 03:37.283
- Why not?
- Because I'm a girl.

03:37.317 --> 03:39.285
That's discrimination,
he can't do that.

03:39.319 --> 03:42.389
He did it, Mama. What's your
big mouth gonna do about it?

03:44.090 --> 03:46.092
We can't let him
get away with this.

03:46.126 --> 03:49.829
And we won't. This is
sexist pigism of
the worst kind.

03:49.863 --> 03:52.232
- But what can we do about it?
- We gotta fight back.

03:52.265 --> 03:55.402
- We'll go right
to the top on this.
- Don't be an idiot, Zack,

03:55.435 --> 03:58.304
President Bush is too busy.

03:58.338 --> 04:01.041
No, you twink,
we'll take it to Mr. Belding.

04:01.041 --> 04:04.844
Underneath it all,
he's a fair-minded,
sensitive man

04:04.878 --> 04:06.312
and a real friend
to the students.

04:06.346 --> 04:09.883
( Belding laughing )

04:09.916 --> 04:11.217
Hello, everybody.

04:11.251 --> 04:13.953
I've got the funniest topic
for my show today.

04:14.054 --> 04:17.089
- What?
- Coach Sonski
says that some girl

04:17.123 --> 04:19.192
came in to try out
for the wrestling team.

04:21.428 --> 04:23.063
Can you believe it?

04:25.065 --> 04:26.866
Here's your food, guys.

04:27.934 --> 04:29.269
Where's mine?

04:29.302 --> 04:31.838
Get it yourself,
Miss Digging for Dirt.

04:31.871 --> 04:33.106
There goes your tip.

04:34.307 --> 04:36.743
Kristy, we're gonna get you
that wrestling tryout

04:36.776 --> 04:39.145
- before you can
say Hulk Hogan.
- What do you mean?

04:39.179 --> 04:42.916
Jessie's about to use
the power of the airwaves.

04:42.949 --> 04:46.186
<i>This is Jessica Spano</i>
<i>for "Spano Speaks."</i>

04:46.219 --> 04:49.389
There were a lot
of snorts and grunts
heard at Bayside yesterday,

04:49.422 --> 04:52.892
and they weren't just from
the sweaty,
red-faced wrestlers.

04:52.926 --> 04:56.129
<i>They were from the snouts</i>
<i>of Bayside's two</i>
<i>biggest sexist pigs,</i>

04:56.162 --> 04:59.132
<i>Coach Sonski</i>
<i>and Principal Richard Belding.</i>

04:59.165 --> 05:02.035
- Kelly: Whoa, be careful.
- Way to go, Jessie.

05:02.035 --> 05:05.905
I'd like to present them
with the Double Swine Award.

05:05.939 --> 05:08.341
( pig snorts )

05:10.043 --> 05:12.379
<i>I say if a woman wants</i>
<i>to wrestle with the grunts,</i>

05:12.412 --> 05:14.080
<i>that's her business.</i>

05:14.114 --> 05:18.218
So, fellow students,
support women's rights.

05:18.251 --> 05:20.320
( pop music playing )

05:21.187 --> 05:23.256
( chanting )

05:26.793 --> 05:30.363
You are too much.
How can I thank
you for all of this?

05:30.397 --> 05:34.134
I'll think
of something interesting.

05:34.167 --> 05:37.170
- ( chanting continues )
- Yo, what's goin' on here?

05:37.203 --> 05:39.439
Get off those mats.
I just had them pressed.

05:39.472 --> 05:41.174
Stop macho pigism!

05:41.207 --> 05:43.443
It is absolute
pandemonium in the gym.

05:43.476 --> 05:46.846
Coach Sonski, how does it feel
to be the most
hated man at Bayside?

05:46.880 --> 05:49.215
Oh, I don't care if I'm hated.

05:49.249 --> 05:52.252
I have pets at home
that love me.

05:52.285 --> 05:54.187
Probably a pig.

05:54.220 --> 05:57.257
No, no, we won't go!
