06:00.894 --> 06:02.929
- No, no, we won't go!
- Hey, hey, hey, hey!

06:03.029 --> 06:05.899
- What is going on here?
- No, no, we won't go!

06:05.932 --> 06:07.801
- No, no, we won't go!
- ( Belding shouting )

06:07.834 --> 06:10.070
- Hey-ey!
- ...we won't go!

06:10.103 --> 06:12.939
A hush falls over the crowd as
the other most
hated man at Bayside

06:13.039 --> 06:16.276
- enters the gym.
- Quiet, please.

06:16.309 --> 06:19.779
You can't shut us up.
We want equal
opportunity for Kristy.

06:19.813 --> 06:21.448
And we're not leaving
until she gets it.

06:21.481 --> 06:24.484
- All: Yeah!
- I mean if that's okay.

06:24.517 --> 06:27.387
Belding, you gonna let these
kids tell you how to
run your school?

06:27.420 --> 06:29.522
Well, of course not.

06:30.256 --> 06:31.758
Am I really hated?

06:31.791 --> 06:34.194
Yes-sssss!

06:34.227 --> 06:36.496
Mr. B, Coach, look,

06:36.529 --> 06:40.233
she says she's
a good wrestler,
why not let her try out?

06:40.266 --> 06:44.204
It's her right as a chick.
I mean as a liberated chick.

06:44.237 --> 06:46.973
Come on, Coach,
why not give her a chance?

06:47.073 --> 06:50.276
Okay, I'm sensitive to dames.
I watch "Oprah."

06:50.310 --> 06:53.279
- All: Yeah!
- Slater: All right, Coach.

06:53.313 --> 06:56.383
But if the little
sweetie gets mangled,
I'm not responsible.

06:57.417 --> 07:00.286
- What do you weigh, honey?
- 110 pounds.

07:00.320 --> 07:01.821
Folks, we have
just witnessed history.

07:01.855 --> 07:04.858
This is
the first girl at Bayside
to admit her weight.

07:04.891 --> 07:06.760
Rodriguez, <i>andale.</i>

07:08.461 --> 07:11.798
Don't worry, little girl,
I won't hurt you.

07:11.831 --> 07:16.136
- Oo-ooh, I'm shaking.
- All right,
take your positions.

07:16.169 --> 07:19.139
Kristy faces a tough test,
Rodriguez is one of Bayside's

07:19.172 --> 07:22.042
best wrestlers
and reigning
nerd-toss champion.

07:22.042 --> 07:25.912
- ( crowd cheering )
- All right. Ready.

07:25.945 --> 07:28.214
- On the whistle.
- ( whistle blows )

07:28.248 --> 07:30.316
( cheering continues )

07:39.592 --> 07:42.962
Do you believe in miracles?
Well, Kristy wins
in a stunning upset.

07:43.063 --> 07:46.566
I hope this doesn't affect
his nerd tossing, Zack.

07:46.599 --> 07:49.903
Look at her,
not a hair out of place.

07:49.936 --> 07:52.439
- Hey,
you're really good, Kristy.
- Thanks.

07:52.472 --> 07:54.374
- What do you think, Coach?
- With you and the babe

07:54.407 --> 07:56.509
