of winning
the league this year.

07:56.543 --> 07:58.511
Welcome to the team, Kristy.

07:59.379 --> 08:02.148
Way to go, Kristy.

08:02.182 --> 08:05.218
- Kristy, you were terrific.
- I couldn't have
done it without you.

08:05.251 --> 08:07.821
We sisters have
to stick together.

08:12.325 --> 08:15.161
- And a special
thanks to you, Zack.
- Well, I...

08:16.296 --> 08:18.031
Hey!

08:19.466 --> 08:22.035
