He was raised by wolves.

08:45.158 --> 08:48.161
- This looks delicious.
- Too bad you can't eat it.

08:48.194 --> 08:51.865
- You're in training now.
- You're right.
You take it, Zack.

08:51.898 --> 08:53.767
- I wouldn't be on
the team without you.
- Well, thanks.

08:53.800 --> 08:56.169
See you later, we gotta
head to the radio station.

08:56.202 --> 08:58.438
- Come on, Screech.
- Oh, wait, Zack,

08:58.471 --> 09:01.441
- are you gonna
eat that wrapper?
- No, why?

09:01.474 --> 09:04.711
After eating wax, there's
nothing like a good wrapper
to wash it down.

09:04.744 --> 09:06.446
( groans )

09:06.479 --> 09:09.015
Get out of here.
Come on.

09:09.015 --> 09:11.418
Jessie, thanks for helping me
make the team.

09:11.451 --> 09:13.887
I just stood up
for what l believed in.

09:13.920 --> 09:17.023
Oh,
she's a cute little feminist,
isn't she?

09:18.458 --> 09:20.160
You're on thin ice, bubba.

09:21.928 --> 09:25.098
Don't you ever
go off duty, girl?

09:25.131 --> 09:27.701
Kristy, that was a great move
you put on Rodriguez.

09:27.734 --> 09:30.036
- Where'd you learn it?
- From you.

09:30.070 --> 09:33.039
You used it on Ninick
in last year's
city championship.

09:33.073 --> 09:36.042
- You saw me?
- You were awesome.

09:36.042 --> 09:38.845
You know, this year
you are gonna be
state champion.

09:38.878 --> 09:42.048
How about that, Mama?
Isn't that great?

09:42.048 --> 09:44.217
Oh, golly, yes.

09:44.250 --> 09:48.088
Would you mind showing me
your best hold sometime?

09:48.121 --> 09:49.823
Yeah, sure.

09:49.856 --> 09:52.792
How about right now?
I'm not busy.

09:52.826 --> 09:56.096
- Do you mind, Jessie?
- No, Jessie doesn't mind.

09:56.129 --> 09:58.064
Nah, she's your biggest
supporter.

09:58.098 --> 10:00.533
Come on,
let's go hit the mats.

10:03.603 --> 10:06.106
Where did everybody go?

10:06.139 --> 10:08.775
Jessie doesn't
care to discuss it.

10:11.878 --> 10:14.714
This is Zack Morris
broadcasting live from a place

10:14.748 --> 10:17.617
where no guy has gone before.
Know where?

10:17.650 --> 10:19.619
- ( screams )
- Oh-ho, you guessed it.

10:19.652 --> 10:22.022
I'm in the girls' locker room.

10:22.055 --> 10:24.758
I'm in no-man's
land to interview
Bayside's newest...

10:24.791 --> 10:27.093
hey, and cutest wrestler,
Kristy Barnes.

10:27.127 --> 10:30.063
Get out of here.
What are you doing?
You're gonna get in trouble.

10:30.096 --> 10:33.566
No risk is too great to
capture the athlete in
her natural habitat.

10:33.600 --> 10:35.602
You're nuts.

10:35.635 --> 10:40.040
Tell me, Kristy,
what's it like being the only
girl on the wrestling team?

10:40.073 --> 10:43.176
It's fun.
The guys are
really nice to me.

10:43.209 --> 10:46.046
Probably because I can
pin most of them.

10:46.079 --> 10:49.215
- Now get out of here.
- Not until we get
a little personal.

10:49.249 --> 10:52.085
Every guy at Bayside
wants to know one thing.

10:52.118 --> 10:53.920
Okay, what's that?

10:53.953 --> 10:58.091
- What kind of guy
does Kristy like?
- Oh, I don't know.

10:58.124 --> 11:01.261
Perhaps the kind of guy
who would sneak into
a girls' locker room?

11:01.294 --> 11:04.230
Maybe. Look, Zack,
I gotta hit the showers.

11:04.264 --> 11:06.332
Hey, no sweat,
we'll just do
the interview in there.

11:06.366 --> 11:08.835
Oh, no we won't!

11:08.868 --> 11:12.672
This is Zack
Morris reporting live
from the promised land.

11:17.210 --> 11:20.313
This has been real fun.
Would you like to
go to the movies tonight?

11:20.347 --> 11:23.817
- Yeah, I'd love to.
- Pick you up at about...
7:30?

11:23.850 --> 11:26.286
- Yeah, okay.
- Zack Morris!

11:26.319 --> 11:28.888
I know you're in here!

11:28.922 --> 11:31.925
And if I catch you in here,

11:31.958 --> 11:35.295
you... are... suspended!

11:36.396 --> 11:38.665
Where are you Morris?!

11:40.000 --> 11:41.835
Morris?

11:41.868 --> 11:45.372
Morris?!
Mor... ris?

11:45.405 --> 11:48.108
- Gotcha!
- ( both scream )

11:51.011 --> 11:55.115
That principal who
was in the girls' locker
room will remain nameless.

11:55.115 --> 11:58.151
And now, I've saved
the juiciest item for last.

11:58.184 --> 12:00.820
- Where does
Lisa get this stuff?
- She's good, Jessie.

12:00.854 --> 12:02.789
She knew about my zit
at the big game.

12:02.822 --> 12:05.358
<i>What school hunk</i>
<i>and lady wrestler</i>
<i>are putting the moves</i>

12:05.392 --> 12:08.728
<i>- on each other</i>
<i>outside the gym?</i>
