12:08.762 --> 12:12.232
<i>Take it from me,</i>
<i>this new couple</i>
<i>is flipping over each other.</i>

12:12.265 --> 12:15.068
- That can't be.
- She wouldn't say
it if it wasn't true.

12:15.068 --> 12:16.970
<i>As you know, I never lie.</i>

12:17.070 --> 12:19.906
<i>I saw them with my own</i>
<i>beautiful brown eyes.</i>

12:19.939 --> 12:24.110
- Are you sure?
<i>- Surely a match</i>
<i>made in heaven.</i>

12:24.144 --> 12:27.147
I don't believe you.
You're lying. You're lying.

12:27.180 --> 12:29.249
( radio static fades )

12:30.750 --> 12:33.286
She's my friend,
but not my best friend.

12:33.319 --> 12:35.422
