those escape holds you
were showing me.

12:42.762 --> 12:44.898
Okay, okay, look,
they're not too hard.

12:44.931 --> 12:48.001
Let's try
the Full Nelson Escape.
Go ahead, put me in one.

12:52.472 --> 12:54.407
( gasps )
Too cool.

12:54.441 --> 12:56.309
All right, now you try it.

13:00.046 --> 13:03.249
Whoa,
that was pretty good, Kristy.
Not bad.

13:03.283 --> 13:05.952
You worked on the Full Nelson
and the Half Nelson,

13:06.052 --> 13:07.354
why don't you show her
the Willie Nelson?

13:09.055 --> 13:11.725
That's a country
and wrestling joke.

13:11.758 --> 13:15.395
I got spurs
that jingle-jangle-jingle.

13:16.730 --> 13:19.165
Can I try the Reverse
Bearhug Escape?

13:19.199 --> 13:20.700
Yeah, sure.

13:20.734 --> 13:23.703
- I wanna get this right.
- Okay.

13:23.737 --> 13:25.905
Good, just hold me tighter.

13:27.173 --> 13:29.376
Wow, you're really strong.

13:30.744 --> 13:32.879
( Jessie screams )

13:35.949 --> 13:39.085
I loved the movie.
So romantic.

13:39.119 --> 13:40.887
Wasn't Michelle Pfeiffer
beautiful?

13:40.920 --> 13:43.089
Compared to you,
she was a bow-wow.

13:43.123 --> 13:45.959
- Come on, Zack.
- No, I mean it, Kristy.

13:45.992 --> 13:49.462
You look so great tonight.
So much like a... like a girl.

13:50.096 --> 13:51.831
I am a girl, you know?

13:51.865 --> 13:55.101
I know all right.
I was watching you more
than the movie.

14:00.140 --> 14:01.941
Well, look who's here.

14:02.042 --> 14:04.844
If it's not Bayside's
big bad lady wrestler.

14:04.878 --> 14:07.180
