just leave us alone?
We're on a date.

14:07.213 --> 14:10.850
Shut up, Morris
or I'll twist
you into a pretzel.

14:10.884 --> 14:12.419
Look,
I don't want any trouble.

14:12.452 --> 14:15.922
Why don't you
go back to Valley
and find your brain?

14:15.955 --> 14:18.725
What's your problem?
Are you nuts? Just chill...

14:20.093 --> 14:22.195
- Are you gonna
leave us alone?
- No.

14:22.228 --> 14:24.330
Oh, ouch, okay.

14:28.068 --> 14:30.070
